'''Tarikhda faca weyn ee Beesha Hubeer.'''
----------------------------------------------
Beesha Hubeer wexey ku abtirsadan oday la oran jiray Hiil Abroone. Hiil Abroone waa shaqsigii ugu horeyay oo yimaada geeska Afrika qasatan deeganada Alto-Jubba oo ah meeshi Somali badankeda ay kasoo faracaantay. Haddaba, Odayga Hiil Abroone la oran jiray wuxu markisa hore ka yimid dhanka iyo wabiga la yirahdo (Tana River) wuxuna ka tirsanna qoomiyada la yirahdo Kushatic (Cushatic) qasatan jufada reer SAAM. Dabcan odaygii Hiil Abroone marku yimaaday dhulka East Afrika oo aheyd dhul iska cidla ah 1,500 sano kahor aya wuxu Hiil Abroone bilaabay innu aqal hoori kaa dhisto mel kamid ah deeganada Alto-Jubba. Haddaba, sanadooyin kadib Odayga Hiil Abroone wuxu dhalay labo wiil oo lagu magacabo SAAM-AALY iyo SAABE-DOW. Dabcan Odayga Hiil Abroone wuxu aha oday karti badan oo hanti badan tabcay sidda xoola nool ee Geela, Ariiga iyo Lo’daa sii aysaan u bahanin ilmaahisa. Haddaba, Odaygii Hiil Abroone markii ilmahiisa aay qaan gareyn oo asagi 89 jir noqday ayu ilmaahisa la dardaarmay sidda hantida dhaxaltooyada ee uu kala qeybsan lahayen labada wiil uu dhalay iyo in ay isku xiirnaadan oo iswaalashadan sii xayaawanka dur-joogta ay iskaaga difacaan wayo dhulka ay ku noolayeen wuxu aha mel iska cidla ah. Dabcan sannado kadib odaygii Hiil Abroone wugeeriyoday labadi wiil uu dhalayne hantidi dhaxaltooyada abahoda uga dhintay ayay si cadaalad ah u kala qeybsadeyn halka wiilka curudka ah ee SAAM-AALY uu qatay Geela, Lo’daa, iyo Ariiga…halka wiilka walaalkiisa ah ee SAABE-DOOW uu qatay dhul beeraadka. Muddo kadib labadi wiil wexey yeeshen qoysaas oo kala daagan laba mel oo kala foog halka kan curuudka ahi ee SAAM-AALY uu deegana dhulka hada lo yaqana Yurkud ee Bakool wuxuuna ku dhalay  9 wiil, halka kan yaraanka ahne ee SAABE-DOOW deegana Jiinka waabiga wuxuna ku dhalay 3 wiil oo qurra. Faraca 9-ka wiil ee SAAM-AALY dhalay waxaa ugu curuudsana wiil la oran jiray Yaaburre wuxuna abihisa SAAM-AALY kaga cawin jiray dhanka xoolo ilaalinta, cano liisida iyo difacida. <br />

Mudo kadib faraca SAAM-AALY aya aad u batay, diinta islaamkana way timid, carabti diinta faafineysay marka ay arken dadka ku noola deeganka Alto-Jubba wexey yirahden yaad tihin? Dadki wexey ku jawaaben “SAAM-AALY”, Carabti wuxu afkooda qabtay "SAAMAALI". Haddaba, odaygii SAAM-AALY marku duqoobay wuxu ku geeriyoday lagunna aasay deeganka Yurkud ee Bakool. Dabcan 8 kamid ah 9-kii will uu dhalay odaygii SAAM-AALY wexey ku kala firxaaden dhamaan deeganada dalka oo dhan "gees ka gees" lakiin waxaa uun Alta-Jubba gar ahan degmada Bakool Ku haray wiilka curuudka aha ee Yaaburre. Haddaba Yabuurre marku qoys yeeshay aya wuxu dhalay wiil wuxuna u bixiyay magaca Cali. Dabcan Cali waxa lagu dhalay isla degmada Bakool gar ahan deegan lagu magacaabi jiray “Haakawe” oo hadder ku taalo degmada manta looyaqano Tiyegloow. Cali marku qaan garay wuxu noqday haantile wuxuna laha beero waweyn iyo xoolo tayo leh. Cali marku qoys yeeshay wuxu dhalay laba wiil wuxuna u bixiyay Hubeer iyo Taawle. Haddaba muddo sannadooyin kadib odaygii Cali marku duqobaay wuxu wilaashisa ee Hubeer iyo Taawle kula dardarmay haddi lacale abaar ka dhacdo Bakool inaysaan ku haakan hal mel oo kaliya balse ay u guuran deeganada barwaaqada tallo. Dabcan kuumanan sanno kadib faraca Hubeer Cali aya aad uu taarmay marka laala barbaardhigo Taawle Cali. Haddaba Hubeer Cali wuxu dhalay 4 wiil waxaana ugu curaadsan “Hiiyaame”, waxa ku xigga “Haraa”, waxa ku sii xigga “Galbiyeed”, yaraanka reerkana wa HULIYE. <br />

Dabcan muddo boqolal sanno kadib aya deeganka Bakool waxaa soo fodsaartay abaar baa'an iyo cunto yarran, Hubeerki iyo walaalkis Taawle wexey go’aan saadeyn inay usoo guuran dhanka iyo Shabellaha hoose oo wagaasi aheyd Janaada adduunka. Haddaba odaygii Hubeer Cali iyo Taawle Cali oo si wadaajir ah usoo guureyn aya hal mar soo wadda galaay gobolka Shabellaha hoose oo waagas aheyd mel iska cidla ah. Dabcan odaygii Hubeer Cali iyo walalkis Taawle Cali marka ay soo gaareen deegganka hada looyaqano Leego ayay isku maacsalaameeyen Hubeer iyo Taawle, halka odaygi Hubeer Cali iyo 4-tisa wiil ay usoo guureen dhanka iyo degmada Daafeet halke Taawle Cali usoo aadday dhanka iyo degmada Qooryoleey.<br />

Dabcan odaygii Hubeer Cali marku Daafeed yimid tuuladi ugu hooreysay uu soo deegay wuxu uu bixiyaay magaca “Haakawe” oo ah magac laga soo musaafuriyay deegankii Tiyeglow oo odaygii Hubeer deeganna ee Haakawe la oran jiray, xitaa mah-mahyo facweyn aya jirtaa oo ah “Hubeer guree, Haakaw Maadhafaw”, tasoo micnaaheydu tahay “Hubeer haddu xita guroo, magaca Haakawe ma iska dhafayoo”. Haddaba, 1,000 sanno kadib markii Hubeer uu deeggana degmada Daafeet aya qar kamid ah Hubeerka ayaa wexey usoo guureen dhanka iyo Qansaxdheere qasatan deeganka Ooflawe oo wagaasi mel cidla aheyd. Haddaba, Hubeerka marku deegana degmada Qaansaxdheere ku dhawaad 900 sanno ayay baateen qar kamid ah wexey isku fiidiyeen deeganada Gedo iyo Jubooyinka oo waggasi aheyd mel duur cidla ah lakin barwaqo aheyd. Haddaba, Hubeerki marku Jubooyinka yimid aya wexey uu suurto gashay inay ka deegan meelo istraateji ah. 


